OL,5, Students on a government-funded work   
OL,6, scheme were placed at a firm run by a  
OL,7, convicted paedophile.                  
OL,9,FDarren Kavanagh, 47, got thousands of  
OL,10,Fpounds for his company via Kickstart to
OL,11,Ftake on students aged 16 to 24 on      
OL,12,FUniversal Credit.                      
OL,14,FHe moved to Somerset during the        
OL,15,Fpandemic after being jailed for two    
OL,16,Fyears in July 2016.                    
OL,18,FThe Department for Work and Pensions,  
OL,19,Fwhich funds the scheme, said it was    
OL,20,F"committed to safeguarding claimants". 
